make that mark over those two pieces of tape,

00:30:40.549 --> 00:30:42.549
critically over that gap between them.

00:30:42.549 --> 00:30:46.460
Take off the two pieces of paint...of tape
rather while the paint is wet still.

00:30:46.460 --> 00:30:47.700
That's fine.

00:30:47.700 --> 00:30:50.500
And you should be left with a very crisp line
in between.

00:30:50.500 --> 00:30:51.809
Many artists use this.

00:30:51.809 --> 00:30:55.139
Piet Mondrian famously did a whole lot of
this.

00:30:55.139 --> 00:30:58.529
